{"tid":596544,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺甸尼 呢類隊長好撚無用","createTime":"2018-03-17T17:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T22:42:40.000Z","uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"570b594c68bf741b2693f855b3bed0d6a256ea19","tid":596544,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:53:13.000Z","msg":"係場上都係支點等波到<br />\n<br />\n守成點唔關你事 提搶激勵又無雷公咁遠<br />\n<br />\n你話牙朗美斯前鋒做隊長 成隊睇你頭 睇得好自然士氣高<br />\n<br />\n呢d前場大舊衰真係唔知有乜用<br />\n<br />\n有波又唔好意思唔比你射<br />\n<br />\n你叫盧卡古去做隊長佢都可能會助下攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb5dd8369ab781b97a75542e7a4db4df8462d13","tid":596544,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:54:59.000Z","msg":"如果佢姓馬就唔同講法"},{"pid":"903980797b5971b263c32135c772f289fbc967d8","tid":596544,"uid":12034,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aeb5dd8369ab781b97a75542e7a4db4df8462d13","tid":596544,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:54:59.000Z","msg":"如果佢姓馬就唔同講法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:58:51.000Z","msg":"呢個又咪比意撚吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9e39b207f78fd4b8e15ef9cf694b17cf715fd8","tid":596544,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:15:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯左馬甸尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f6ed934180172cb17213cf91d01b304cda3cf0","tid":596544,"uid":150109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T22:42:40.000Z","msg":"法國神軒仲無用<br />\n坐係後備席激勵隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}